#

Classic New York Style Cheeseburger with Crispy Fried Onions and House-Made Pickles

$15.99
850 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

AmericanBeefGourmetBBQ

Description

A juicy beef patty topped with melted cheese, crispy fried onions, and tangy house-made pickles on a toasted bun, delivering the ultimate comfort food experience.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef (80/20): 1 lb
  • Cheddar Cheese: 4 slices
  • Burger Buns: 4
  • Yellow Onions: 2
  • All-Purpose Flour: 1 cup
  • Buttermilk: 1 cup
  • Pickles (sliced): 1 cup
  • Vegetable Oil: for frying
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Garlic Powder: 1 tsp
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
